Global Health Advisory:  The Department of State advises U.S. citizens to avoid all international travel due to the global impact of COVID-19.  Many areas throughout the world are now experiencing COVID-19 outbreaks and taking action that may limit traveler mobility, including quarantines and border restrictions. Even countries, jurisdictions, or areas where cases have not been reported may restrict travel without notice.    Read More Country-Specific Information: Government of Zimbabwe Lockdown Entry and Exit Requirements: Quarantine Information Distributed by APO Group on behalf of U.S. Embassy in Zimbabwe. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .